{"tid":1780932,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人準備靠得力素維生","createTime":"2019-12-12T18:44:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T05:15:31.000Z","uid":341659,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aac2ac98febb9644eb67dcd77cecc684e7904fa2","tid":1780932,"uid":341659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:44:37.000Z","msg":"個人成日暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全身冇力 企唔住 眼花<br />\n有時食粒糖會好返小小<br />\n有時食半盒得力素都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭地鐵企得耐 同埋<br />\n去人多/焗嘅地方都會奶嘢<br />\n要即刻搵位坐唔係就暈低<br />\n最唔想係麻煩到身邊嘅人<br />\n要即刻搵位坐 有時仲嚇親佢哋<br />\n做運動更加唔洗講<br />\n跑一陣都暈低睇唔到嘢發冷<br />\n不過坐返5分鐘就會好<br />\n其實好困擾<br />\n有朋友搞聚會去多人嘅哋方都唔想去<br />\n飲小小酒都會即暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇嚟以後只可以摺喺屋企<br />\n人生已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff77e65d0d1d5e024ced51fb12fc53c5c58455e1","tid":1780932,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"打個J會唔會好D"},{"pid":"b2d2d3a6079d0c6a9a3970f1cf85621b065b797d","tid":1780932,"uid":341659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ff77e65d0d1d5e024ced51fb12fc53c5c58455e1","tid":1780932,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"打個J會唔會好D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"j都冇力打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39938311762a5a3f4f1c070af7d7cf04fc0e8aa7","tid":1780932,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2d2d3a6079d0c6a9a3970f1cf85621b065b797d","tid":1780932,"uid":341659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ff77e65d0d1d5e024ced51fb12fc53c5c58455e1","tid":1780932,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"打個J會唔會好D"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"j都冇力打<img src=\